{"tid":1586670,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"盧卡古奠勝 國米2：0贏米蘭打吡","createTime":"2019-09-22T05:27:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T09:21:07.000Z","uid":54373,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"16352e95269628de6f0808d0e73b949917659300","tid":1586670,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T05:27:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/kQfGICwVsvlpJNFDehvENA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2019-09/c4d2e730-dcdd-11e9-aedf-6a26d2ffbd74\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FkQfGICwVsvlpJNFDehvENA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-09%2Fc4d2e730-dcdd-11e9-aedf-6a26d2ffbd74&h=a5076346&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n盧卡古奠勝 國米2：0贏米蘭打吡<br />\n<br />\n國際米蘭由盧卡古（Romelu Lukaku）、拿奧達路馬天尼斯合組雙箭頭，中場有辛斯壓陣，翼鋒阿歷斯山齊士先列後備。AC米蘭以4-3-1-2陣式出戰，由比安迪、蘇素、里奧爭入球。 雙方甫開賽就鬥得激烈，18分鐘，拿奧達路馬天尼斯妙傳，盧卡古左腳射地波，門將當拿隆馬瞓身救出；3分鐘後，馬天尼斯施射，當拿隆馬撲出不遠，翼鋒迪岩布斯奧補射中柱彈出。兩隊其後各食一次詐糊，以0:0完半場。 49分鐘，A米守將突然發夢，造就中場波索域施射省中中場基斯彈入網，國米領先1:0。61分鐘，拿奧達路馬天尼斯在左路射門，當拿隆馬擋出，盧卡古近門頂斜。盧卡古在78分鐘終於破門，把中場巴利拿的傳中頂入，為國米奠定2:0勝局。"},{"pid":"917f4e8d60b4b75745820821da88d07cabd2e0a0","tid":1586670,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T05:56:43.000Z","msg":"瘦左好多"},{"pid":"9575275f1b069ccd2414e439c127b947b4063000","tid":1586670,"uid":42246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T05:58:16.000Z","msg":"今年有冇機會國米vs曼？<br />\n<br />\n想睇渣古報牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01ae384d8ad458eb09c945918ed228e9976e7548","tid":1586670,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9575275f1b069ccd2414e439c127b947b4063000","tid":1586670,"uid":42246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime